OL,7,FITV West Country reporter Max Walsh
OL,8,Ftries on the empathy suit being used
OL,9,Fin Bristol
OL,11,FA care home in Bristol has purchased a
OL,12,Fsuit which simulates dementia to help
OL,13,Fits staff understand what residents
OL,14,Fare experiencing.
OL,16,FThe empathy suit is made up thirteen
OL,17,Fcomponents including goggles,
OL,18,Fheadphones, weighted vests and pads,
OL,19,Fwhich inhibit movement, vision and
OL,20,Fhearing.
