OL,7,FAround 100 staff at Brunelcare's
OL,8,FDeerhurst Care Home have now
OL,9,Fexperienced the suit, with some
OL,10,Fdescribing the training as the "best
OL,11,Fthey have ever had".
OL,13,FThe training is now being offered to
OL,14,Ffamilies of loved ones with dementia
OL,15,Fand other care homes.
