OL,3,CCare staff try 'fascinating' dementia
OL,4,Csuit to help them empathise with
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,FLesley Hobbs, manager, said: "The suit
OL,8,Fis amazing and so insightful. The
OL,9,Fdementia empathy suit has weights
OL,10,Faround the ankles and knee pads to
OL,11,Frestrict the movement and speed of the
OL,12,Fwearer.
OL,14,F"There are tinted goggles that affect
OL,15,Fthe wearer's peripheral vision
OL,16,Falongside the colours around them.
