OL,7,F"The gloves that are worn are
OL,8,Fconnected to a machine that makes
OL,9,Fhands shake, meaning control of
OL,10,Fmovements and coordination were thrown
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,F"It was fascinating, and I believe all
OL,14,Fof our carers should experience the
OL,15,Fsuit as part of an induction process."
OL,17,FOur reporter's experience - Max Walsh
