OL,3,CCare staff try 'fascinating' dementia
OL,4,Csuit to help them empathise with
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,F"My task involved walking outside to
OL,8,Fsit in a car - something elderly
OL,9,Fresidents at Deerhurst Care Home do
OL,10,Fevery day. But wearing the suit made
OL,11,Fthis simple exercise painfully slow.
OL,13,F"The suit was put on in five minutes
OL,14,Fwith the help of two trainers, but
OL,15,Fimmediately trying to hold a
OL,16,Fconversation became very difficult.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
