OL,3,CCare staff try 'fascinating' dementia
OL,4,Csuit to help them empathise with
OL,5,Cresidents
OL,7,F"My final challenge was to attempt to
OL,8,Fwrite a birthday card. Yet, with
OL,9,Fgloves that were causing my hands to
OL,10,Fshake, my writing was illegible and I
OL,11,Fcould not even put the card in the
OL,12,Fenvelope.
OL,14,F"The whole experience was eye-opening
OL,15,Fto what so many elderly have to cope
OL,16,Fwith. It was a huge relief to take the
OL,17,Fsuit off after only fifteen minutes!"
